name: CSSPageRule
description: CSSPageRule is an interface representing a single CSS @page rule. It implements the CSSRule interface with a type value of 6 (CSSRule.PAGE_RULE).

members.name: CSSPageRule.selectorText
members.description: Represents the text of the page selector associated with the at-rule.

members.name: CSSPageRule.style
members.description: Returns the declaration block associated with the at-rule.
